title: Hour 3 - Premier League Kickoff with Rebecca Lowe
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Premier League Kickoff with Rebecca Lowe
description:
Dan chats with Rebecca Lowe of NBC Sports Soccer to get you ready for the start of Premier League this weekend. Dan calls BS on LIV Golf refusing to add more golfers.
